definition.value: A galloyl-beta-D-glucose compound having a galloyl group at the 1-position.
A glycerone 3-phosphate having an unspecified O-acyl substituent at the 1-position.
An primary alcohol that is butan-1-ol in which a hydrogen at position 3 has been replaced by a methyl group.
A cephalosporin having an acetoxy group at the 3-position and a 5-carboxy-5-oxopentanamido group at the 7-position.
